config HUAWEI_LP_SENSORS_AP3426
	tristate "AP3426 3-in-1 digital ALPS+PS+IRLED sensor driver"
	depends on I2C
	default n
	help
	  Say Y here if you want to enable the AP3426 ALPS sensor driver.
